These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-1::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, drawing, card-games
There are 3 different favourite colors: light-blue, grey, mauve
1. the person who's hobby is baking is the person who likes grey##1
2. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
3. the person who likes mauve is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is drawing##3
4. the person who likes grey is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |
| Hobby   | baking | card-games | drawing    |
| Color     | grey    | mauve       | light-blue |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-2::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, aconite, marigold
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, salsa, jazz
1. the fan of country is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
2. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
3. the fan of country is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who growsaconite is the fan of jazz##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |     2     |     3      |
| Flower     | marigold | amaryllis | aconite  |
| Music-Genre   | country  | salsa  | jazz |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-3::.
There 3 different types of food: potato, apricot, raspberry
There are 3 different nationalities: pakistani, british, canadian
1. the british is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person eating potato is on the far right##1
3. the person eating apricot is the canadian##1
4. the british is on the right of the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Food           | raspberry | apricot | potato |
| Nationality   | pakistani        | canadian    | british        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-4::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, weightlifting, cycling
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, bongani, alhambra
1. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
2. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
3. the dannemann-smoker is between the person who's sport is cycling and the alhambra-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Sport   | cycling | weightlifting | lacrosse |
| Cigar     | bongani  | dannemann    | alhambra  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-5::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, soccer, badminton
There 3 different types of food: garlic, pepper, nectarine
1. the person eating nectarine is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3
2. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
3. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is between the person who's sport is soccer and the person eating nectarine##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |
| Sport   | soccer | lacrosse | badminton |
| Food     | pepper   | garlic   | nectarine   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-6::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, dannemann, aristoff
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, punk, classical
1. the fan of classical is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
2. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
3. the aristoff-smoker is on the left or right of the davidoff-smoker##3
4. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the fan of punk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |   2    |     3      |
| Cigar   | aristoff | davidoff | dannemann      |
| Music-Genre     | punk  | classical | dubstep |

