.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-7::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, snowmobile, scooter
3 different pets are kept: lizard, bird, guinea-pig
1. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the person driving the snowmobile##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |     3      |
| Transport   | snowmobile  | scooter    | boat       |
| Pet   | bird | guinea-pig | lizard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-8::.
City: berlin, london, edinburgh
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, blend, bolivar
1. the person traveling to berlin is the dannemann-smoker##1
2. the blend-smoker is in the middle##1
3. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
4. the person traveling to london is on the left or right of the dannemann-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |   3    |
| City   | edinburgh        | london  | berlin   |
| Cigar       | bolivar | blend | dannemann |

