.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-10::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, singing, drawing
3 different games are played: whist, poker, billiard
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3
2. the person playing billiard is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |
| Hobby      | camping | singing    | drawing      |
| Game   | poker       | whist | billiard |

