.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-11::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, september, november
There are 3 different favourite colors: ebony, chestnut, fuchsia
1. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
3. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
4. the person who likes chestnut is on the left or right of the person who likes fuchsia##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |      2       |       3        |
| Birthday   | november | september         | december          |
| Color        | ebony | chestnut | fuchsia |

