.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-13::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, thriller, horror
House: farmhouse, futuristic, victorian
1. the farmhouse house is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the futuristic house##1
3. the victorian house is between the futuristic house and the farmhouse house##2
4. the farmhouse house is the person watching thriller movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | horror | thriller |
| House           | futuristic    | victorian    | farmhouse       |

