3. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1
4. the person eating corn is the colonial house##1
5. the person eating zucchini is on the left or right of the cape-cod house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |     3     |
| House   | farmhouse | cape-cod | colonial |
| Food   | zucchini     | spinach  | corn    |

