2. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
4. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
5. the owner of the rabbit is the person who growsazalea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |       3       |
| Pet       | horse | rabbit | guinea-pig |
| Flower   | marigold  | azalea   | amaryllis    |

