.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-20::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: basketball, biathlon, lacrosse
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, june, september
1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
3. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |      3      |
| Sport      | lacrosse    | biathlon | basketball         |
| Birthday   | september | june  | december |

 